{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"56bfccbe1c","title":"朱简文的右派言论","origin":"《右派言论集》（河南医学院马列主义教研室编印，1958年4月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4123b17232","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"56bfccbe1c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"00d8e3d85b","name":"河南医学院"},{"id":"43f130f3ae","name":"朱简文"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3d31d5dd8a","type":"title","text":"朱简文的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56bfccbe1c"},{"id":"3a6aaed410","type":"authors","text":"河南医学院朱简文","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56bfccbe1c"},{"id":"8e1ea35537","type":"subtitle","text":"(朱简文：河南医学院会计科会计)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56bfccbe1c"},{"id":"ff14c959ec","type":"paragraph","text":"镇反时党的宽大政策是假的，真的坦白了该杀的还是杀，共产党可以籍口不杀不足以平民愤来搞。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56bfccbe1c"},{"id":"3fa1f210fd","type":"paragraph","text":"党在运动中是不忠实的，共产党统治一切。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56bfccbe1c"},{"id":"58cd5a8bf4","type":"paragraph","text":"三反思想改造交待材料，一遍两遍通不过，在精神上受到很大的创伤，肃反运动也是如此太残忍了一些，这到底是谁不忠诚不老实，而是相信投机的勇敢分子害人不浅。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56bfccbe1c"},{"id":"457c6be672","type":"paragraph","text":"农业合作化“左倾”完成了农业合作化任务，所以发生供求矛盾，要不是毛主席，不知人饿死多少人。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56bfccbe1c"},{"id":"1a3c373798","type":"paragraph","text":"党比反革命罪更大，整风的办法和风细雨，本身就是宗派主义，肃反平白把人打骂一顿，官僚主义造成的损失不比肃反中的重点罪恶大吗？为什么要和风细雨，反正政权在手愿咋搞咋来。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56bfccbe1c"},{"id":"51c7a5ee16","type":"paragraph","text":"整风开始是：“知无不言，言无不尽；言者无罪，闻者足戒”，现在变成了“知不敢言，言不敢尽，闻者记账，言者挨整”。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56bfccbe1c"},{"id":"c25fda8225","type":"paragraph","text":"×××在反右派的掩护下贩卖私货，拿别人给共产党献礼，想藉此早点入党。拥护党的人都是随声附和。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56bfccbe1c"}],"page":{"id":"9cdc4c3f57","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"56bfccbe1c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}